@baseurl = http://127.0.0.1:3000

### get all books

http://127.0.0.1:3000/books

### add book 
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/books HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Start with Why",
  "author": "Simon Sinek"
}

### get book id 1
GET  http://127.0.0.1:3000/books/1 HTTP/1.1


